    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Here's a quick sample using the <code>DecimalFormat</code> class mentioned by Nick.</p>\n\n<pre><code>float f = 12.345f;\nDecimalFormat df = new DecimalFormat(\"#.00\");\nSystem.out.println(df.format(f));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The output of the print statement will be 12.35. Notice that it will round it for you.</p>\n"
