    "question_id" : 5195837,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was looking for an answer to this question and later I developed a method! :) A fair warning, it's rounding up the value.</p>\n\n<pre><code>private float limitDigits(float number) {\n    return Float.valueOf(String.format(Locale.getDefault(), \"%.2f\", number));\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
