    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use Decimal format if you want to format number into a string, for example:</p>\n<pre><code>String a = &quot;123455&quot;;\nSystem.out.println(new \nDecimalFormat(&quot;.0&quot;).format(Float.valueOf(a)));\n</code></pre>\n<p>The output of this code will be:</p>\n<p>123455.0</p>\n<p>You can add more zeros to the decimal format, depends on the output that you want.</p>\n"
